OL,5,G1235 James Martin's Islands to
OL,6,G     Highlands
OL,7,     FJames is joined by chef Galton
OL,8,     FBlackiston for a tour of Cornwall,
OL,9,     Fsampling some world-class ice
OL,10,     Fcream and cooking fresh seafood
OL,11,     Ftapas with chipotle dressing. The
OL,12,     Ftrip concludes with a visit to
OL,13,     FSennen beach, where they practice
OL,14,     Ftheir oil painting and break out
OL,15,     Fthe barbecue
